 \vec{n} = -\frac{\partial z}{\partial x}\hat{i} - \frac{\partial z}{\partial y}\hat{j}+\hat{k} = \frac{x\hat{i}+y\hat{j}+za^2\hat{k}}{za^2} 
 \frac{1}{||\vec{n}||} = \sqrt{\frac{z^2a^4}{x^2+y^2+z^2a^4}} 
